{"tid":578860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：我永遠都準備好戰鬥","createTime":"2018-03-03T04:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T08:46:51.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9f38009434edae74de5fa077ccc5801b42548fe4","tid":578860,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴在五天內先後於英格蘭聯賽盃決賽和英超吞下曼城六隻光蛋，令球隊繼續陷於低潮。不過，兵工廠領隊雲格仍然躊躇滿志，希望靠自己豐富的經驗挽救球隊繼續下沉，他又表示自己「永遠都準備好戰鬥」。<br />\n<br />\n該名法國籍領隊說：「我對目前的情況當然感到失望，但我曾經歷過這一切，過往的經驗、改變現況和繼續幫助球隊的決心有助走出困局。」阿仙奴目前落後英超第4名的熱刺十分，球隊可能要在餘下賽季全勝才有望重返前4，但雲格已經預告，周日作客白禮頓一戰會輪換球員，確保下周中在歐霸盃16強首回合鬥AC米蘭時，可以精銳盡出。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴中場韋舒亞因為輕微的足踝問題缺席了對曼城的聯賽，他在周五亦未有操練。雲格透露，如果他在周六復操的話，仍會被考慮列入作客白禮頓的大軍名單。"},{"pid":"b6f4dc1ac173f1ce02d334eb35224205fabb3a85","tid":578860,"uid":137361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41b437ea868d6adc1ef7e175969bf541d5e17fd1","tid":578860,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"屢敗屢戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3bd0787e08ebb1d060c66e527abb36b8b5dd29","tid":578860,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b12960a58f617f7b964e15c58bbd30f6a681566","tid":578860,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"搏歐霸"},{"pid":"b63af3c3309a4144477f3f66e87de42d6781d714","tid":578860,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb41be9a7421c67d42acb62b2d63c751401dc99","tid":578860,"uid":55,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32fcdfff2cb51d184d6461016cedb321ce1a1e59","tid":578860,"uid":165124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"落場踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4820568d72497238dbec7604a833393e5b0420","tid":578860,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"若結果偏不如意始終無悔<br />\n拚命過去追求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f926f73cbb75ed66064c6b37f453f45184db8ca1","tid":578860,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺不死！"},{"pid":"6dab6ece3ef5b26740656d9bb75c3f5b925d9312","tid":578860,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b12960a58f617f7b964e15c58bbd30f6a681566","tid":578860,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"搏歐霸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"今季開頭先話歐霸冠軍唔應該有得踢歐聯 , 佢贏左既話應該會自動棄權"},{"pid":"5c90d3cfb58e2873bd61e1d04599ef649810516c","tid":578860,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/132631_cd331b6bb66a09608f6c1919ac426713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F132631_cd331b6bb66a09608f6c1919ac426713.jpg&h=36535362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3dc81a61ac5cdc971d6c93cb7eb008c3939c8ff","tid":578860,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b437ea868d6adc1ef7e175969bf541d5e17fd1","tid":578860,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"屢敗屢戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"屢戰屢敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211fae543f4b15ae4bfd3a27fbb97a4b00f841c0","tid":578860,"uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4b12960a58f617f7b964e15c58bbd30f6a681566","tid":578860,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"搏歐霸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"【暗寸摩佬？】雲格：我反對歐霸盃冠軍入歐聯<br />\n2017-08-07 10:26:47  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　上個賽季的英超聯賽，阿仙奴屈居第五無緣歐冠盃。而曼聯拿到了第六，不過由於摩連奴的球隊獲得了歐霸盃的冠軍，因此曼聯新賽季也獲得了一個歐冠盃名額，而阿仙奴只能去踢歐霸盃了。阿仙奴教練雲格對於歐洲足協的這種制度非常不屑，他認為歐霸盃冠軍不該獲得一個歐冠盃名額。<br />\n　　雖然新賽季阿仙奴也要出戰歐霸盃了，不過雲格對於歐霸盃冠軍獲得歐冠盃資格的規定並不讚同。雲格說：「我一直反對這樣做。因為這些年除了曼聯，奪得歐霸盃冠軍的球隊總是那些歐冠盃小組賽出局的球隊。你不能在賽季一開始就想著靠歐霸盃奪冠重返歐冠盃。」<br />\n　　「我一直不支持這樣做。因為我覺得這樣的想法會影響你在聯賽的表現。試想一下，如果一支球隊在四月份時認為有更多的機會拿到歐霸盃冠軍，他們可能會放棄一些聯賽的比賽，不會專注於聯賽的競爭了。」"},{"pid":"a75629781d169f7b2ca200bcfdae7c1dc32ab786","tid":578860,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/p_lDOjLt634/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fp_lDOjLt634%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=002b1168&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f22a88f80f4a665c4537d6c0e4200f8b017a4a18","tid":578860,"uid":36497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題係反雲狗太多</blockquote><br />\n日反野反 無撚哂士氣啦 <br />\n反雲狗我屌你媽西！"},{"pid":"325b959e9c5617954590b734eba2b374013795db","tid":578860,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"人生太短出手要更大<br />\n雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193a46f52cfcb6413f574453be70dcb765cacdd5","tid":578860,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴今時今日究竟有幾多內憂外患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成績<br />\n<br />\n球員續約<br />\n<br />\n錢<br />\n<br />\n領隊<br />\n<br />\n黃綠軍醫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雲加一個人掌哂權但搞到隊波仲難搞過中型班咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}